ODM leader Raila Odinga said on Tuesday that he supports the proposal to extend car grants to ward representatives announced by President Uhuru Kenyatta last week.
Mr Odinga said that he understands the challenges the local leaders go through.
During a meeting with MCAs in Sagana last week, the President promised to push for Sh2 million car grant for the ward representatives.    



